<h2 id="movie-cards">Movie cards</h2>
<p>Quick look movie cards were designed to show key information about each movie including the genre, rating and a short synopsis.</p>

<figure><img src="/images/projects/imdb/imdb-card.jpg" alt="Deadpool movie card" class="fixed" /></figure>

<h2 id="icon-glyphs">Icon glyphs</h2>
<p>The icon glyphs across the website needed to be consistent so I created a set of icons to accompany various elements of the website.</p>

